input.command:
sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claude-code-claimdb/test_dbs/california_schools.sqlite" "
SELECT f.CDSCode, f.\`School Name\`, 
       f.\`Free Meal Count (K-12)\`, 
       f.\`Enrollment (K-12)\`,
       f.\`Free Meal Count (K-12)\` * 100.0 / f.\`Enrollment (K-12)\` AS pct_free
FROM frpm f
JOIN schools s ON f.CDSCode = s.CDSCode
WHERE s.County = 'Los Angeles'
  AND s.Charter = 0
  AND f.\`Enrollment (K-12)\` > 0
  AND (f.\`Free Meal Count (K-12)\` * 100.0 / f.\`Enrollment (K-12)\`) < 0.18
ORDER BY pct_free;
"
